            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school is excellent,\n\nbut some teachers in the management, along with a person named Manu Bhardwaj, are taking a significant amount of money (approx 1.5 lakhs) for admissions.\n\nPlease avoid them. The school's father should take strict action against this.\n\nThere are also other teachers in the school involved in this. Manu Bhardwaj is a fraudulent individual who will take money from you under the pretext of securing admission in any school and then deceive you.\n\nRespected Father, please pay attention to the management of the school Branches.\n\nThanks",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
