          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Father Agnel School is a well-respected institution in Noida, known for its commitment to providing a high-quality education to its students. The school boasts a dedicated and experienced faculty, and offers a wide range of academic programs that are designed to challenge and inspire students. The school's state-of-the-art facilities and modern infrastructure provide an ideal learning environment, and the school's extracurricular activities and sports programs offer opportunities for students to develop their talents and interests outside of the classroom. The school's values of discipline, hard work, and character-building are well-inculcated in the students and the school has a strong reputation for producing well-rounded and successful graduates. Overall, Father Agnel School is an excellent choice for parents who are looking for a high-quality education for their children.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Fr. Agnel School - Khora Colony,Sector 62A"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Shubham Kumar"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-03-12",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is one of the oldest schools of Noida, affiliated to CBSE board. The school has tremendous focus on extra curricular, and the teachers are experienced and well versed. The helper staff here is also simple and trust worthy. The school playground is lush green, with a separate basket ball court and a swimming pool. The school takes extra precautions for the safety of children, with a helper designated at each floor, security camera in each class and elevated railings along the staircases. All Pre primary buses are owned by the school, whereas most of the other buses are contractual. Quality of buses is an area, where the school can give little more focus. Else, you are lucky if your child is in this school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        }
